brands.description: Coroplast is a brand name of corrugated plastic and a registered trademark of Coroplast, LLC, a member of the Inteplast Group of companies. Because of the success of this brand, it has become a generically used tradename and many people in North America today refer to all corrugated plastic as "coroplast". A similar product is marketed in Australia under the brand name Corflute.

transcript.text: Hello everyone, we are in very uncertain time.
The whole world is going through the tough time.
Everyone is looking for the ways and opportunities to grow through and beyond COVID-19.

Even now globally an economy is picking up post lockdown, businesses and people are getting back to work in many countries and many of our client initially experienced a slow down in their businesses and their order volume also gone down drastically.
So few of our successful client researched and created special COVID-19 product categories which are in demand.

They introduced many of the products for the very first time and with the help of web to be technology, they were able to quickly change their offerings and introduce new products quickly as per the shifting market and end customer needs.
So here we would like to share few of the on pins of successful clients who are very successful during COVID-19.
Many of them quickly launched in the B2C and B2B online storeference and generated great sales from existing B2B clients.
Anyone attracted many new clients requiring COVID-19 products.
They quickly changed their banners and introduced wide entropy products online.
Many of the products they launched when pre designed such as social distancing product where many clients create a innovative range of products to help businesses maintain social distancing.
For products like signs and banners, our clients created wide range of ready to buy designs for clients to quickly pick up and order online without any hassles.
Even products like safety signs, speakers, floor, locals, posters, benign banners, they created wide range so people can pick up and order online.
And even some of the trade shows, specialized printers created innovative booth with sanitizers, dispensers and standard banners to help organize outdoor events.
And many clients offered personalized products such as mask where one can personalize it online with the images and logo using an online designer studio.
Even products like the art science, graduate science, safety signs.
But any small business owner who does not have a professional designers or who who's not who does not know how to design can pick up the ready template at custom logo and text and order online.
So even in lockdown with regular businesses were down, few of our clients were very busy and generated online sales.
Even one of our clients shared that they had record-breaking sales during COVID-19 in the month of active.
Even the other clients shared that they acquired many new clients because they offered unique COVID-19 products online.
You do can quickly easily set up and offer these range of products within a week.
So if you're a print business and if you want to offer about products, contact us at WWW dot on printshop.com and our support team will help you quickly set up and launch the solution.
Thank you.
